"DENKI KAMINARI, QUIRK: ELECTRIFICATION"
Ngomong-ngomong, apa kalian tidak merasa

60
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:57,700
"TSUYU ASUI, QUIRK: FROG"
di Kelas B banyak yang istimewa?

61
