dapat memperkuat Quirk.

67
00:04:13,450 --> 00:04:15,000
Mencatat lagi.

68
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,000
Deku juga berkembang pesat.

69
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,290
Baguslah jika benar begitu.

70
00:04:18,290 --> 00:04:20,700
Meski tak bisa dibandingkan denganku.

71
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:21,910
Masa?

72
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:23,870
Aku bukan membicarakan tinggi badan, oke?

73
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:29,910
"ALL MIGHT, QUIRK: ONE FOR ALL"
Aku diam-diam kemari.

74
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:31,540
All Might.

75
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:33,409
Midoriya, kemari sebentar.

76
00:04:33,409 --> 00:04:34,500
Baik.

77
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,200
Bulan madu?

78
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:40,620
Rasanya belakangan ini,
Midoriya sering bersama All Might.

79
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:45,080
Sejak festival budaya, sepertinya dia
minta All Might mengawasi latihannya.

80
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:48,790
Uraraka memang hebat,
tahu segalanya tentang Midoriya.

81
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:52,580
Aku... aku hanya dengar kata orang,
sepertinya begitu adanya.

82
00:04:53,370 --> 00:04:54,659
Ma... maaf.

83
00:04:54,659 --> 00:04:56,909
Jangan gunakan Quirk sebelum pertandingan.

84
00:04:56,909 --> 00:04:58,790
Jangan gunakan kekuatan fisik.

85
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:00,750
Seperti sedang breakdance.

86
00:05:02,290 --> 00:05:03,870
Midoriya...

87
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:06,660
